== Frontend ==

Pre-requisites, install:

    node-js/npm
    npm install -g brunch bower
    gem install bundler

cd frontend
bower install
npm install
./bower_assets.sh
bundler install


After this can run front-end server which will reload automatically if change anything in frontend/app/*

    brunch w -s


